<descript>
<abstract>This dataset is intended for read-only use. The purpose of these data is to provide display, identification, and analysis tools for determining current boundary information for Forest Service managers, GIS specialists, and others.</abstract>
<purpose>This dataset represents boundaries of areas that have distinct management or use authorities, or agreements for USDA Forest Service action. These areas include Cost Share Agreement Areas, Exchange Authority Areas, Land Adjustment Plan Areas, Land Management Planning Units, Forest Reserves, and Secretary's Order Areas.</purpose>
</descript>
